(4, 1, 1, '<p>We are an athletic training facility that mixes a little old school with the new school! We biomechanical approach to movement to maximize movement pattern efficiency which in return maximizes power output and encourages healthy movements!</p>\r\n<p>All of our instructors and trainers played college or pro sports which allows us to provide first hand experience and study each sport extensively to continue are knowledge on maximizing the performance of our athletes!</p>', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:57:17', '2022-01-05 21:34:51', NULL),
(5, 1, 1, '<p>We are an athletic training facility that mixes a little old school with the new school! We biomechanical approach to movement to maximize movement pattern efficiency which in return maximizes power output and encourages healthy movements!</p>\r\n<p>All of our instructors and trainers played college or pro sports which allows us to provide first hand experience and study each sport extensively to continue are knowledge on maximizing the performance of our athletes!</p>', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 19:06:46', '2021-12-21 19:06:46', NULL),
(9, 1, 2, '<h3>Mobility</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hip External Rotation</li>\r\n	<li>Hip Internal Rotation</li>\r\n	<li>Shoulder External Rotation</li>\r\n	<li>Shoulder Internal Rotation</li>\r\n	<li>Shoulder Pronation</li>\r\n	<li>Ankle Dorsiflexion</li>\r\n	<li>Ankle Plantarflexion</li>\r\n	<li>Spine Rotation</li>\r\n	<li>Hamstring</li>\r\n	<li>Overhead Squat</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Strength/Athleticism</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Grip Strength</li>\r\n	<li>Abductors</li>\r\n	<li>Adductors</li>\r\n	<li>Deadlift</li>\r\n	<li>Bicep</li>\r\n	<li>Tricep</li>\r\n	<li>Back</li>\r\n	<li>Chest</li>\r\n	<li>Shoulder</li>\r\n	<li>Calf</li>\r\n	<li>Broad Jump</li>\r\n	<li>20 Yard Sprint</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Hitting</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High Speed Video Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Exit Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Launch Angle</li>\r\n	<li>Attack Angle</li>\r\n	<li>Hand Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Launch Quickness</li>\r\n	<li>Kinetic Chain</li>\r\n	<li>Timing</li>\r\n	<li>Rhythm</li>\r\n	<li>Point of Contact</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Pitching</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High Speed Video Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Spin Rate</li>\r\n	<li>Spin Direction</li>\r\n	<li>Spin Efficiency</li>\r\n	<li>Vertical Break</li>\r\n	<li>Horizontal Break</li>\r\n	<li>Release Angle</li>\r\n	<li>Release Height</li>\r\n	<li>Separation</li>\r\n	<li>Timing</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 15:06:56', '2021-12-21 15:06:56', NULL),
(10, 3, 1, '<p>Our staff is second to none! All of our instructors not only have playing experience at the highest levels, but also have the knowledge and background to use the advanced technology at BB Sports. We take our vast experience and pair it with our state of the art facility to give you the best training in Northern Colorado.</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 15:16:39', '2021-12-21 15:19:36', NULL),
(11, 4, 1, '<p>Our top of the line program!!! This is our pride and joy program that is built from programs like the New York Yankees, Toronto Blue Jays, Los Angeles Dodgers, Washington Nationals, Colorado Rockies, Miami Marlins, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use technology such as hittrax, rapsodo, diamond kinetics, and more. Included is a full Athletic Performance Evaluation testing mobility, strength, and sports specific skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Train like the Professionals!!!</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 16:03:45', '2021-12-21 16:06:12', NULL),
(12, 4, 2, '<p>Train in a 1 on 1 or 2 on 1 setting. We offer hitting, pitching, fielding, catching, speed and agility, and strength training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All of our instructors and trainers have a background in baseball and softball and played at the collegiate and/or pro level. We use technology such as hittrax, rapsodo, diamond kinetics, and more.</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 16:14:56', '2021-12-21 16:14:56', NULL),
(13, 4, 3, '<p>Can&rsquo;t make it into the facility? No problem!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have online lessons at the palm of your hand. Our head instructor has been doing video analysis for youth, high school, college, and pro athletes for the last 5 years with over 5000 hours of video analysis work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He has been working with brand new and veteran athletes at BB Sports for 3 years developing some of the best drill progressions. These drill progressions are designed to fix any flaws in the quickest and most efficient ways</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 16:16:28', '2021-12-21 16:16:28', NULL),
(14, 4, 4, '<p>Recruiting Services</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Get access to the knowledge and resources needed to get recruited!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We build recruiting videos, give you email templates, add you to our Player Portal, and talk you through the process of sending videos and information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t miss out on getting recruited by not being proactive or not knowing where to start. Let us help!!</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 16:18:25', '2021-12-21 16:18:25', NULL),
(15, 5, 1, '<p>This is our top of the line training program for serious athletes that are looking to play college and pro ball!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is our highly advanced training program that focuses on the skills, biomechanics, and mobility/strength needed to preform at the highest level!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Must be willing to commit to a weekly commitment at a determined time that best fits instructors and athletes/family.</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 16:43:21', '2021-12-21 16:43:21', NULL),
(16, 5, 2, '<h2>Hitting</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase&hellip;</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exit Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Distance</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(Bat Path, Hand Path, Spine Stability, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Consistency</li>\r\n	<li>Pitch Recognition</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 17:40:19', '2021-12-21 17:52:55', NULL),
(22, 5, 3, '<h2>Fielding</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase&hellip;</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Footwork</li>\r\n	<li>Glove Work</li>\r\n	<li>Glove Work</li>\r\n	<li>Awareness</li>\r\n	<li>Bad Hop Reactions</li>\r\n	<li>Pre Pitch Planning</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:01:39', '2021-12-21 18:01:39', NULL),
(23, 5, 4, '<h2>Velocity and Pitching</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase&hellip;</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Throwing Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Spin</li>\r\n	<li>Leg Drive</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(arm action, hand position, shoulder alignment, hip rotation, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Control</li>\r\n	<li>Offspeed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:02:55', '2021-12-21 18:02:55', NULL),
(24, 5, 5, '<h2>Strength, Speed, and Power</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>Increase&hellip;</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Mobility</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Strength</li>\r\n	<li>Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Agility</li>\r\n	<li>Explosion</li>\r\n	<li>Power in Multiple Planes</li>\r\n	<li>Body Awareness</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:04:22', '2021-12-21 18:04:22', NULL),
(25, 5, 6, '<h2>Youth Athleticism</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase&hellip;</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hand Eye Coordination</li>\r\n	<li>Motor Skills</li>\r\n	<li>Strength</li>\r\n	<li>Agility</li>\r\n	<li>Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Acceleration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:05:31', '2021-12-21 18:05:31', NULL),
(26, 5, 7, '<p>We are looking for committed athletes that are wanting to elevate their game to that next Peak Top and continue their passion for the game.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have you fill out a form that gives us the best days and times to fit your schedule and our schedule! We have groups running almost everyday!!</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:05:57', '2021-12-21 18:05:57', NULL),
(27, 6, 1, '<p>Forget the cookie cutter programs!!! At BB Sports we do everything custom to each athlete!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full Athletic Performance Evaluations are done for each one of our athletes!! We test mobility, strength, and sports specific skills to design the perfect progression that is custom to each athlete!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use the most advanced technology available to track numerous metrics. Hittrax, Rapsodo, 4D motion, Pocket Radar, Strength Sensors, etc. are all used to get the most accurate numbers possible to track and design programs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hitting, Pitching, Velocity, Fielding, Catching, Strength, and Speed/Agility are all offered and run by instructors with college or pro experience!</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:29:41', '2021-12-21 18:29:41', NULL),
(28, 6, 2, '<h2>Hitting</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exit Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(Bat Path, Hand Path, Spine Stability, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Consistency</li>\r\n	<li>Pitch Recognition</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fielding</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fielding Percentage</li>\r\n	<li>Rhythm</li>\r\n	<li>Footwork</li>\r\n	<li>Glove work</li>\r\n	<li>Bad Hop Reactions</li>\r\n	<li>Bad Hop Reactions</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Strength/Mobility Speed/Explosion</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobility</li>\r\n	<li>Strength</li>\r\n	<li>Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Agility</li>\r\n	<li>Explosion</li>\r\n	<li>Power in Multiple Planes</li>\r\n	<li>Body Awareness</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:34:17', '2021-12-21 18:34:17', NULL),
(29, 6, 3, '<h2>Pitching/Velocity</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Throwing Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Spin</li>\r\n	<li>Leg Drive</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(arm action, hand position, shoulder alignment, hip rotation, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Control</li>\r\n	<li>Offspeed</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pitching/Velocity</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Blocking</li>\r\n	<li>Framing</li>\r\n	<li>Footwork</li>\r\n	<li>Foot Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Pop Times</li>\r\n	<li>Transfer Times</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:36:59', '2021-12-21 18:36:59', NULL),
(30, 7, 1, '<p>Our head instructor Shea Bell has done over 5000 hours of coaching and video analysis. He works with 10+ pro athletes, 20+ college athletes, and numerous high school and college athletes. Including players such as Chad Bell(3B, Yankees), JD Hammer(P, Phillies), Aaron Ochsenbein(P, Dodgers), Shane Matheny(IF, Giants), Ben Newton(C, ECU), and so many more</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:52:21', '2021-12-21 18:52:21', NULL),
(31, 7, 2, '<h3>1) Skills and Mobility Analysis</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Every client starts their first lesson with sending us 1 thing for breakdown and analysis</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hitting or Pitching Video</p>\r\n\r\n<p> &lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Side view is the best for optimal analysis</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:55:48', '2021-12-22 00:00:16', NULL),
(32, 7, 3, '<h3>2) Easy Video Upload with APEX by Upper Hand</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Upload your videos all within APEX just by creating an account or having us create it for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You submit your video and within 48 hours you have a breakdown, analysis, and lesson plan</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:56:37', '2021-12-21 18:56:37', NULL),
(33, 7, 4, '<h3>3)Top of the Line Evaluations</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our evaluations are always extremely in depth. I take the time to look at multiple angles(if provided) to find the most alarming issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> &lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Hitting or Pitching Video &lt;br /&gt;Side view is the best for optimal analysis</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 18:58:43', '2021-12-22 00:01:00', NULL),
(34, 7, 5, '<h3>4) Lesson Plans</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our lessons are custom to each clients&hellip;we take the same process every time to find out why we are struggling and how to get better</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Send in your video</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;We analyze your swing or throwing motion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Voiceover analysis explaining what we see</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;We send list of drills with videos examples and how to fix</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Message us if you have questions on the drills we sent</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 19:03:27', '2021-12-21 19:03:27', NULL),
(35, 7, 6, '<h3>5) Multiple Ways to Pay</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our 3 packages allow you to train at your pace. Find out what your doing wrong or stay consistent with</p>\r\n\r\n<p>multiple lessons&hellip;as low as $21 per lesson</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;1 Lesson=$30</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;4 Lessons=$100</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-futbol-o&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;8 Lessons=$175</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 19:04:57', '2021-12-21 19:04:57', NULL),
(36, 8, 1, '<p>Our youth teams the Colorado Yetis(Baseball) and Colorado Power(Softball) are some of the top programs in Northern Colorado.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We give the kids the basic fundamentals and athleticism to play any sport as far as they would like</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 19:36:30', '2021-12-21 19:36:30', NULL),
(37, 8, 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Develop individual skills that will help each player have success at every level</li>\r\n	<li>To learn game knowledge and situations taught at the professional level</li>\r\n	<li>To create athleticism and hand eye coordination that will help with all sports</li>\r\n	<li>To develop a passion for this great game and experience life lessons and experiences with your friends and BB Sports family</li>\r\n	<li>And overall to develop young men that will have success in life whether it is on the field or in life</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 19:38:26', '2021-12-21 19:38:26', NULL),
(39, 8, 4, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Lessons and Training Included in Team Fees</li>\r\n	<li>State of the Art Facility</li>\r\n	<li>Lessons from Pro and College Coaches</li>\r\n	<li>Top of the line gear and jerseys</li>\r\n	<li>15% off Marucci/Victus/Old Hickory Items</li>\r\n	<li>15% off all BB Sports additional Memberships, Lessons, and Apparel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 19:42:29', '2021-12-21 19:42:29', NULL),
(40, 8, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>&lt;span class=&quot;b-art-points-icon&quot;&gt; &lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-dot-circle&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;Hittrax&lt;/span&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;span class=&quot;b-art-points-icon&quot;&gt; &lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-dot-circle&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;Rapsodo&lt;/span&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;span class=&quot;b-art-points-icon&quot;&gt; &lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-dot-circle&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;4D Motion&lt;/span&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;span class=&quot;b-art-points-icon&quot;&gt; &lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-dot-circle&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;Diamond Kinetics&lt;/span&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;span class=&quot;b-art-points-icon&quot;&gt; &lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-dot-circle&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;Stalker Radar Guns&lt;/span&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;span class=&quot;b-art-points-icon&quot;&gt; &lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-dot-circle&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;Full Lifting Gym&lt;/span&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;span class=&quot;b-art-points-icon&quot;&gt; &lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-dot-circle&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;Access Whenever&lt;/span&gt;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 19:44:52', '2021-12-21 19:44:52', NULL),
(41, 9, 1, '<p>BB Elite is a college showcase and prep team for high school level baseball and softball athletes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is not your typical travel ball team. We run our teams exactly like a college program in order to prepare them for the next level</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is not your typical travel ball team. We run our teams exactly like a college program in order to prepare them for the next level</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 19:50:53', '2021-12-21 19:50:53', NULL),
(43, 9, 2, '<h3>Our Goals</h3><ul>\r\n	<li>Develop individual skills that will help each player have success at every level</li>\r\n	<li>To get college exposure and experience playing some of the best talent in the country</li>\r\n	<li>To learn game knowledge and situations taught at the professional level</li>\r\n	<li>To experience the country, colleges, and baseball all around the country to get a feel for where you want to play college ball</li>\r\n	<li>To develop a passion for this great game and experience life lessons and experiences with your friends and BB Sports family</li>\r\n	<li>And overall to develop young men that will have success in life whether it is on the field or in life<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 20:02:59', '2021-12-22 01:05:58', NULL),
(44, 9, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Play at places like Vanderbilt University, Kansas State University, Wichita State University, University of Dallas, University of Louisiana Monroe, and more</li>\r\n	<li>Lessons and Training Included in Team Fees</li>\r\n	<li>State of the Art Facility</li>\r\n	<li>Pro and College Coaches</li>\r\n	<li>Recruiting Help and Guidance</li>\r\n	<li>15% off Marucci/Victus/Old Hickory Items</li>\r\n	<li>15% off all BB Sports additional Memberships, Lessons, and Apparel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 20:04:33', '2021-12-21 20:04:33', NULL),
(45, 9, 4, '<h3>Our State of the Art Facility</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hittrax</li>\r\n	<li>Rapsodo</li>\r\n	<li>4D Motion</li>\r\n	<li>Diamond Kinetics</li>\r\n	<li>Stalker Radar Guns</li>\r\n	<li>Full Lifting Gym</li>\r\n	<li>Access Whenever</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 20:07:31', '2021-12-21 20:07:31', NULL),
(46, 10, 1, '<p>Our youth teams the Colorado Yetis(Baseball) and Colorado Power(Softball) are some of the top programs in Northern Colorado.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe in training sessions both on the field, in the cage/bullpen, and in the gym in order to give the kids the basic fundamentals, knowledge and athleticism to play any sport as far as they would like</p>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 20:35:48', '2021-12-21 20:35:48', NULL),
(47, 10, 2, '<h3>Our Goals</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Develop individual skills that will help each player have success at every level</li>\r\n	<li>To learn game knowledge and situations taught at the professional level</li>\r\n	<li>To create athleticism and hand eye coordination that will help with all sports</li>\r\n	<li>To experience the country, colleges, and baseball all around the country to get a feel for where you want to play college ball</li>\r\n	<li>To develop a passion for this great game and experience life lessons and experiences with your friends and BB Sports family</li>\r\n	<li>And overall to develop young men and woman that value skills/attributes such as respect, hard work, passion, confidence, accountability, and morality that will help them in all aspects of life</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 20:37:28', '2021-12-21 20:37:28', NULL),
(48, 10, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Lessons and Training Included in Team Fees</li>\r\n	<li>State of the Art Facility</li>\r\n	<li>Lessons from Pro and College Coaches</li>\r\n	<li>Top of the line gear and jerseys</li>\r\n	<li>Recruiting Help and Guidance</li>\r\n	<li>15% off Marucci/Victus/Old Hickory Items</li>\r\n	<li>15% off all BB Sports additional Memberships, Lessons, and Apparel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 20:38:57', '2021-12-21 20:38:57', NULL),
(49, 10, 4, '<h3>Our State of the Art Facility</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hittrax</li>\r\n	<li>Rapsodo</li>\r\n	<li>4D Motion</li>\r\n	<li>Diamond Kinetics</li>\r\n	<li>Stalker Radar Guns</li>\r\n	<li>Full Lifting Gym</li>\r\n	<li>Access Whenever</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 0, '2021-12-21 21:02:12', '2021-12-21 21:02:12', NULL);

